{{Quote|The '''battle madness''' of my people is a fearsome, fearful thing&mdash;a berserker rage that transforms one into a super-Human, nigh-irresistible killing machine.|[[Aron Peacebringer]]|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 54">[[Star Wars (1977) 54|''Star Wars'' (1977) 54]]</ref>}}
'''Ryastraad''', otherwise known as '''battle madness''' was a state of rage or berserk that members of the [[Calian]] species would enter into on certain occasions. The state of ryastraad gave the individual almost super-Human powers. [[Aron Peacebringer]] went into battle madness when he thought that [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] had been killed by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]], and was capable of breaking the thick metal chain that he was shackled in.

